{"tid":1403742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙街坊小事一樁","createTime":"2019-08-03T21:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T21:45:13.000Z","uid":262842,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"abdef17ca4eb4569bf509545e9d4c45135a959c1","tid":1403742,"uid":262842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:38:52.000Z","msg":"啱啱發夢係黃大仙打游擊<br />\n打到三面防暴包抄<br />\n係時候Be Water<br />\n我係龍翔道嗌對面即將被包嗰啲人過對面上慈雲山嗰邊散<br />\n<br />\n有啲Full Gear (唔知算唔算勇武)<br />\n問點解要散 話唔需要散㗎<br />\n有個重過嚟捉實我隻手好燥咁問我<br />\n「唔明點解要散？散去邊啫？唔通翻屋企啊？」<br />\n緊係啦 大家街坊裝 重食完彈 高空襲物完一大Round<br />\n唔通企係到等人夾咩<br />\n呢到最大優勢就係近屋企 隨時出過嚟都重得<br />\n我同佢講我地俾人包緊 至少退去安全地方Be Water<br />\n重有聽日重85重有大把日子慢慢報呢一仇<br />\n<br />\n結果佢應唔到我 但佢好燥 個樣應該重想叫人留<br />\n然後我俾fd拉走左<br />\n我想講<br />\n師兄請不要燥 嗰陣退係正確嘅<br />\n我地完全冇打陣地嘅能力<br />\n你地著晒Full Gear嘅都唔喺前面擋 點叫我地唔走<br />\n最多慢慢退 同街坊一齊撤<br />\n但冇可能留低頂 做肉盾<br />\n<br />\nPs.下次可以冷靜啲傾 唔洗燥到傾唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPps. 你手套應該食過椒/催淚 你捉實完我手臂之後乸左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃大仙人好波！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7cbcdcd9111a2f63d3b55bfa1822f7552653e5","tid":1403742,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:39:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港九新界，遍地開花，東西夾擊，光復荃灣</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n荃灣啲廢老唔食下煙唔識醒，狗總隔離集醫院，民居，學校，地鐵站，商場於一身，再加上地理位置四通八達。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日港島區奮戰，新界都唔可以衰俾人睇</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一站，光復荃灣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c9c2ebcbdaa902682863947c380b64585333509","tid":1403742,"uid":10402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:40:42.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},{"pid":"3e1f6e470d94477454dc0972b79e8b8e05c5d8c2","tid":1403742,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:40:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係時候轉下玩法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同狗打 對政府冇影響 <br />\n對真係揸權嘅土共更加冇影響<br />\n要一針見血 就要搵政權最著緊嘅野同佢玩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">錢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動全面升級] 不論和理非/勇武，入一入嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"070f20b212cfb73545d5f5d48bfa2947cd543090","tid":1403742,"uid":262842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c9c2ebcbdaa902682863947c380b64585333509","tid":1403742,"uid":10402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:40:42.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T21:45:13.000Z","msg":"多謝師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}